creator: App Mobile Group
descriptionHtml:
Directions Maps is free application.
•You can search any location around the world.
•Find nearby such as: Find restaurants near me,AT M,Airport,Bank,Bar, Beauty Salon,Book Store,Bus Station,Car wash,Casino,Clothing Store,Coffee,Dentist,Doctor,Establishment,Hotel,Food,Gas Station,Grocery or Supermaket,Hospital,Library,Movie Theater,Museum,Night Club,Park,Police,Restaurant,School,Shopping mall,Spa,Store,Subway Station,Taxi Stand,Train Station,Travel Agency,University,Zoo.
Navigation maps:The App voice guidance for route finder. Walk guidance takes you every step of the way.
Directions Map use material design technology .The user interface very great.
This the app is a navigation tool designed for helping people when travelling to different city. It displays places near to user's current location based on selected category.

FEATURES :
Street maps: you can street view at any location.
Find places near me: ATM,Coffee,bank etc.(app will show list places you can choose it).
Show your current location on maps,share location by image or address to networks social.
Route planner,Find Router : draw route finder from your current location to any location or app can find from location A to B anywhere on the world.
GPS tracker location when the internet turn off.(Show your current location on maps and tracker’s location)
View maps: Hybrid,Normal,Satellite, TERRAIN...
Remind Me Notifications for all the places you select to remind when you are in vicinity of the place..
View contact details, address,times, distance,rating,image and location of each place.
Other details: website, phone,share link,open hours,list images,comments,suggest,router...->you can order products.
Transit ,compass...

If you have any questions or You want to help for directions maps.Please contact to us via email: mappmobilevn@gmai.com

App Mobile Group.

Thank all.

title: Directions Map - Route Finder

creator: Navigate Traffic - Maps Directions
descriptionHtml:
Directions maps is an application use to find route from my location to other location on maps. It also route finder with compass map. Here is newest feature we has been provided free for you.
After a time , maps route finder back again with great function such as distance map calculator and find route near by example: find atm near me or find restaurant near by. You need to turn on gps on your phone to show exactly latitude and longitude on maps in the real-time.
Features:
- Compass maps : If you using compass for direction you need to note symbols.
+ W is the west
+ E is east
+ S is the south
+ N is the north
This the application support with device have sensor. The compass app depends on the performance of your device exactly. If the compass works perfectly, it means that your sensors are perfect, too.
- Show True North
- Show latitude longitude
- Show level
- Show Magnetic Field Power
- Show Altitude Speed
- Show Sensor State
Direction maps you can search any location around the world. With gps technogogy it will help you find current location on maps in the realtime easily. Location map also tool helpfull voice guidance for route finder, walk guidance takes you every step of the way.
This the app is a navigation tool designed for helping people when travelling to different city. It displays places near to user's current location based on selected category.
Maps distance calculator: Here is tool to distance measurement between citites or any location you want to measure. The application will auto calculate and figure out result exactly.
Find places near me: if you want to make thing to eat you can search with find restaurant near me or find food near by. Direction maps application will auto show list near you and distance measure to that location. Beside you can street view at that location.
If you have any questions or you want to help for directions maps application. Please contact to us via email: mappmobilevn@gmai.com
App Mobile Group.
Thank all.
